{{DISPLAYTITLE:Ceiling_LowerToFloor}} {{Special|254|tag, speed|Ceiling|LowerToFloor}}
* ''tag'': Tag of affected sector * ''speed'': How quickly the ceiling moves
==Usage==
Lowers a ceiling to the height of the floor underneath it. If ''tag'' is 0, then the sector on the line's back side is used.
==Examples==
{{noexamples}}
